SPOILER ALERT

"The Avengers’ first-ever adversary is the Asgardian god of mischief, Loki, who attempts to rule the Earth, aided by an invading Chitauri army. 
Loki was, in fact, working at the behest of the Mad Titan, Thanos, who would formulate new plans in the wake of Loki’s defeat." 

-- Marvel.com
